Bahobaho nikala muna Muhe wa Mulungu, na bahobaho nikala na chigoda cha chifalume kuulanga, na munhu imwe kakala mchanyha yake.
Na munhu ija yakalile mchanyha yake kakala fana langi ya yaspi na zambali. Na chigoda chiyazunguluke chigoda icho chikala fana mvula ya zambalidi, na chihanga chake chikala fana lubiki.
Maabaho kukala na vigoda malongo mane na vine vili chitemela chiyazunguluka chigoda icho, na muna ivigoda ivo wakala walala walala malongo mane na wane, wayawale viwalo vizelu chwee, na mitwi yawo wakala na kombelo za zahabu.
